Heaviside step function with broadcasting:
 
>>> x1 = np.array([-1.5, 0, 2.0])
>>> x2 = np.array([0.5, 0.5, 0.5])
>>> np.heaviside(x1, x2)
array([ 0. ,  0.5,  1. ])

